about.summary: A collection of various R functions for the purpose of Luminescence dating data analysis. This includes, amongst others, data import, export, application of age models, curve deconvolution, sequence analysis and plotting of equivalent dose distributions.

name: r-luminescence
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.9.14" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-luminescence
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Luminescence_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/Luminescence/Luminescence_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 79cf370b693aa72df1aa3d04f73aee19083dc96a1c09b378e00360c4a3e0f9bc

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  skip: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}            # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}      # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-deoptim >=2.2_5
    - r-rcpp >=1.0.5
    - r-rcpparmadillo >=0.10.1.0.0
    - r-xml >=3.99
    - r-bbmle >=1.0.23
    - r-data.table >=1.13.2
    - r-httr >=1.4.2
    - r-lamw >=2.0.0
    - r-magrittr >=1.5
    - r-matrixstats >=0.57.0
    - r-minpack.lm >=1.2_1
    - r-plotrix >=3.7
    - r-raster >=3.4_0
    - r-readxl >=1.3.1
    - r-shape >=1.4.5
    - r-zoo >=1.8
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-deoptim >=2.2_5
    - r-rcpp >=1.0.5
    - r-rcpparmadillo >=0.10.1.0.0
    - r-xml >=3.99
    - r-bbmle >=1.0.23
    - r-data.table >=1.13.2
    - r-httr >=1.4.2
    - r-lamw >=2.0.0
    - r-magrittr >=1.5
    - r-matrixstats >=0.57.0
    - r-minpack.lm >=1.2_1
    - r-plotrix >=3.7
    - r-raster >=3.4_0
    - r-readxl >=1.3.1
    - r-shape >=1.4.5
    - r-zoo >=1.8

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('Luminescence')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('Luminescence')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=Luminescence
  license: GPL-3.0-only
  summary: A collection of various R functions for the purpose of Luminescence dating data analysis. This includes, amongst others, data import, export, application of age models, curve deconvolution, sequence analysis and plotting of equivalent dose distributions.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
